HBnB Project – Technical Documentation
1. Introduction
Purpose and Scope

This document provides the technical documentation for the HBnB Evolution application. It describes the architecture, system design, core entities, and interactions between components. The goal is to provide a clear reference for developers, maintainers, and stakeholders to understand how the system is structured and how its components interact.

Project Overview

HBnB Evolution is a simplified property rental platform inspired by Airbnb. The application allows users to create accounts, list properties, leave reviews, and manage amenities associated with places.

The system follows a modular layered architecture and applies object-oriented programming principles to ensure scalability, maintainability, and separation of concerns.

